## Phase Closeout Protocol

Every phase MUST end with a closeout pass (see `phases.mdc` for full protocol). In short:
1. Refactor & simplify — dead code, duplication, naming
2. Productionize — no debug artifacts or hacks
3. Tests — green, updated, new coverage
4. Lint & format — zero warnings
5. Build — clean
6. Docs — SOUL.md, README, next-session.mdc, phases.mdc all updated
7. Commit — concise message summarizing deliverables

